1
00:00:38,200 --> 00:00:39,280
Zhou Rong is not playing tricks.

2
00:00:39,280 --> 00:00:40,040
How so?

3
00:00:40,600 --> 00:00:43,090
♪ Bunny, bunny, bunny, bunny,
bunny, bunny ♪

4
00:00:43,970 --> 00:00:45,270
♪ Love you, love you, love you ♪

5
00:00:46,850 --> 00:00:49,390
♪ Bunny, bunny, bunny, bunny,
bunny, bunny ♪

6
00:00:47,240 --> 00:00:48,360
20 million.

7
00:00:48,790 --> 00:00:50,320
They can't get that much
from the bank this early.

8
00:00:50,130 --> 00:00:51,580
♪ Love you, love you, love you ♪

9
00:00:50,990 --> 00:00:52,720
They can only find people
to scrape it together.

10
00:00:52,720 --> 00:00:53,610
♪ Oh, gimme ♪

11
00:00:52,840 --> 00:00:54,670
These people are all here
to deliver money.

12
00:00:54,670 --> 00:00:56,650
♪ Dance me in the richness ♪

13
00:00:57,810 --> 00:00:59,400
♪ Raining, make it rain ♪

14
00:00:59,870 --> 00:01:02,510
♪ Oh, cash is my revolution ♪

15
00:02:33,400 --> 00:02:36,970
[Born with Luck]

16
00:02:37,070 --> 00:02:40,010
[Episode 22]

17
00:02:40,130 --> 00:02:44,710
[Sanjiangkou People's Hospital]

18
00:02:50,079 --> 00:02:51,280
You stay here and keep watch.

19
00:02:51,280 --> 00:02:52,810
Don't let anyone get close.

20
00:02:52,870 --> 00:02:53,400
Yes, sir.

21
00:02:55,710 --> 00:02:56,280
Who is it?

22
00:02:56,280 --> 00:02:57,540
Wh-What are you doing?

23
00:03:02,430 --> 00:03:04,090
I didn't do anything illegal.

24
00:03:06,040 --> 00:03:06,770
Chief Zhang.

25
00:03:07,560 --> 00:03:08,870
I was fast asleep.

26
00:03:09,240 --> 00:03:11,100
My heart is racing from the shock.

27
00:03:12,750 --> 00:03:14,480
What's going on, Captain Wang?

28
00:03:15,310 --> 00:03:16,630
You...

29
00:03:17,079 --> 00:03:17,750
Me?

30
00:03:21,030 --> 00:03:22,150
Yes, you.

31
00:03:22,190 --> 00:03:22,710
Me?

32
00:03:31,970 --> 00:03:33,500
We found a set of bianzhong.

33
00:03:34,980 --> 00:03:36,980
Does it have anything to do with you?

34
00:03:37,900 --> 00:03:38,579
No.

35
00:03:42,310 --> 00:03:42,960
Really.

36
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:51,260
I'm not interested in that kind of stuff.

37
00:03:53,750 --> 00:03:54,950
Really, Chief Zhang.

38
00:03:55,000 --> 00:03:56,730
I'm not into that kind of thing.

39
00:03:57,310 --> 00:03:58,570
Really, Captain Wang.

40
00:04:01,150 --> 00:04:01,840
"Zhong"—the end—

41
00:04:01,840 --> 00:04:03,500
signifies bad luck after all.

42
00:04:08,080 --> 00:04:08,810
Makes sense.

43
00:04:09,120 --> 00:04:09,920
Get some rest.

44
00:04:16,390 --> 00:04:17,790
Watch what you're doing.

45
00:04:21,620 --> 00:04:22,430
Chief Zhang!

46
00:04:23,120 --> 00:04:24,720
You can't treat me like this!

47
00:04:33,540 --> 00:04:34,790
Am I dreaming?

48
00:04:41,210 --> 00:04:44,610
[First Inpatient Department]

49
00:04:49,680 --> 00:04:50,920
Turn off all the headlights.

50
00:04:50,920 --> 00:04:51,390
Be quiet.

51
00:04:51,390 --> 00:04:53,210
Don't disturb the people resting.

52
00:04:53,210 --> 00:04:54,230
Get in the car.

53
00:04:57,960 --> 00:05:01,560
[First Inpatient Department]

54
00:05:03,830 --> 00:05:04,560
Chief Zhang.

55
00:05:04,920 --> 00:05:06,050
What are we here for?

56
00:05:07,270 --> 00:05:08,400
What are we here for?

57
00:05:10,430 --> 00:05:12,190
To make Zhou Rong suspect Lang Bowen.

58
00:05:12,190 --> 00:05:13,520
I thought so too before.

59
00:05:13,600 --> 00:05:14,220
But...

60
00:05:14,240 --> 00:05:15,680
Haven't we used this trick before?

61
00:05:15,680 --> 00:05:16,600
How many times have we used it?

62
00:05:16,600 --> 00:05:17,330
Three times.

63
00:05:17,750 --> 00:05:18,810
You think

64
00:05:19,000 --> 00:05:19,800
all is fair in war.

65
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:20,830
Exactly because we've used it—

66
00:05:20,830 --> 00:05:21,950
and we used it 3 times—

67
00:05:21,950 --> 00:05:22,630
Zhou Rong is very likely

68
00:05:22,630 --> 00:05:23,830
to have anticipated what we anticipated.

69
00:05:23,830 --> 00:05:24,580
But he won't anticipate

70
00:05:24,580 --> 00:05:26,780
that we anticipated his anticipation.

71
00:05:27,690 --> 00:05:29,490
Zhou Rong is about to make a move?

72
00:05:38,340 --> 00:05:43,590
[Police]

73
00:05:52,310 --> 00:05:52,770
Rong...

74
00:05:54,640 --> 00:05:56,460
[Come on—What if it's funny?]

75
00:06:22,660 --> 00:06:25,370
[Health and longevity]

76
00:06:27,220 --> 00:06:27,750
Dad.

77
00:06:29,630 --> 00:06:30,120
Mom.

78
00:06:31,600 --> 00:06:32,650
I am unfilial.

79
00:06:35,800 --> 00:06:36,760
This parting...

80
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:42,840
Old man.

81
00:06:43,070 --> 00:06:44,620
They say you raise a son
so they can

82
00:06:44,620 --> 00:06:46,350
take care of you in your old age.

83
00:06:46,430 --> 00:06:48,550
Have our son drive back

84
00:06:48,580 --> 00:06:51,260
and take you to see the doctor,
okay?

85
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:53,870
No need.

86
00:06:54,840 --> 00:06:56,510
He works in a big company.

87
00:06:56,870 --> 00:06:58,110
He's very busy.

88
00:06:59,120 --> 00:06:59,720
Let's...

89
00:07:00,390 --> 00:07:02,640
Let's not cause him trouble.

90
00:07:07,700 --> 00:07:10,190
This is a million US dollars...

91
00:07:30,830 --> 00:07:31,390
Dad.

92
00:07:31,950 --> 00:07:33,140
I'm back.

93
00:07:34,120 --> 00:07:35,580
You're coughing so badly.

94
00:07:35,680 --> 00:07:37,480
Why don't you go to the hospital?

95
00:07:38,070 --> 00:07:39,870
I'll go buy you some cough syrup.

96
00:07:52,220 --> 00:07:53,970
[Lower your head]

97
00:08:04,740 --> 00:08:10,990
[Lower your head]

98
00:08:18,410 --> 00:08:22,750
[Lower your head]

99
00:08:27,830 --> 00:08:28,270
Hello?

100
00:08:30,070 --> 00:08:30,680
Ren?

101
00:08:36,789 --> 00:08:37,850
The money's ready?

102
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:39,000
The money is in the car.

103
00:08:39,000 --> 00:08:39,929
You can count it.

104
00:08:39,950 --> 00:08:40,480
Let's go.

105
00:08:41,270 --> 00:08:42,870
Mr. Zhou, take your medicine first.

106
00:08:42,870 --> 00:08:43,200
Here.

107
00:08:49,310 --> 00:08:50,600
There's one more thing.

108
00:08:50,600 --> 00:08:51,000
What?

109
00:08:51,030 --> 00:08:52,270
Zhang Yi'ang went to the hospital

110
00:08:52,270 --> 00:08:53,870
to see Lang Bowen last night.

111
00:08:56,150 --> 00:08:57,320
What did they talk about?

112
00:08:57,320 --> 00:08:58,050
I'm not sure.

113
00:08:58,480 --> 00:08:59,120
I heard the hallway

114
00:08:59,120 --> 00:09:00,590
was guarded by the police.

115
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:02,000
Only Zhang Yi'ang

116
00:09:02,030 --> 00:09:03,510
and Wang Ruijun went into the room.

117
00:09:03,510 --> 00:09:05,240
They left without saying much.

118
00:09:11,510 --> 00:09:12,390
Also, Du Cong

119
00:09:12,390 --> 00:09:13,480
just called.

120
00:09:13,910 --> 00:09:14,410
He said

121
00:09:14,440 --> 00:09:15,840
they found Li Penggai's car,

122
00:09:15,840 --> 00:09:17,040
and the money is in it.

123
00:09:19,630 --> 00:09:20,080
Okay.

124
00:09:20,670 --> 00:09:21,870
Tell them all to come!

125
00:09:29,910 --> 00:09:31,240
It's Li Penggai, right?

126
00:09:32,030 --> 00:09:33,520
Gai, what happened?

127
00:09:34,270 --> 00:09:34,840
I'm fine.

128
00:09:35,390 --> 00:09:36,200
Open the small gate for me.

129
00:09:36,200 --> 00:09:36,750
Okay.

130
00:09:40,480 --> 00:09:40,910
Okay.

131
00:09:41,790 --> 00:09:42,480
Lock it up.

132
00:09:42,600 --> 00:09:42,930
Good.

133
00:09:44,390 --> 00:09:45,990
Li Penggai just went inside.

134
00:09:48,360 --> 00:09:50,020
This is going to be a good show.

135
00:10:08,470 --> 00:10:09,000
Mr. Zhou.

136
00:10:09,510 --> 00:10:09,960
Ren.

137
00:10:16,200 --> 00:10:17,200
They snatched

138
00:10:17,320 --> 00:10:17,920
the money?

139
00:10:19,550 --> 00:10:20,850
They stole the car too?

140
00:10:23,080 --> 00:10:24,080
According to you,

141
00:10:25,000 --> 00:10:27,400
those two junk collectors are just losers.

142
00:10:28,870 --> 00:10:30,070
You had a knife on you,

143
00:10:30,550 --> 00:10:31,720
yet you got knocked out

144
00:10:31,720 --> 00:10:33,580
and got your money and car stolen.

145
00:10:35,860 --> 00:10:38,060
Do you think anyone would believe that?

146
00:10:39,670 --> 00:10:40,690
Think I'm a fool,

147
00:10:40,720 --> 00:10:41,030
huh?

148
00:10:41,030 --> 00:10:41,860
No, no. I...

149
00:10:41,960 --> 00:10:42,790
I-I remember now.

150
00:10:42,790 --> 00:10:43,200
I remember.

151
00:10:43,200 --> 00:10:43,960
It wasn't them. It wasn't them.

152
00:10:43,960 --> 00:10:44,550
Then who was it?

153
00:10:44,550 --> 00:10:45,030
Well...

154
00:10:47,960 --> 00:10:49,030
When it happened,

155
00:10:50,750 --> 00:10:52,550
one of them was on this side of me,

156
00:10:52,670 --> 00:10:54,330
and the other was on this side.

157
00:10:54,840 --> 00:10:55,790
It wasn't them.

158
00:11:00,000 --> 00:11:01,150
There must be someone else.

159
00:11:01,150 --> 00:11:02,880
There has to be another person!

160
00:11:03,910 --> 00:11:04,670
So you're saying,

161
00:11:04,670 --> 00:11:05,750
with your skills,

162
00:11:05,910 --> 00:11:07,120
you didn't even notice

163
00:11:07,120 --> 00:11:07,750
that there was someone else

164
00:11:07,750 --> 00:11:08,950
in such a small space?

165
00:11:10,720 --> 00:11:11,580
He's an expert.

166
00:11:12,030 --> 00:11:12,960
Super fast too.

167
00:11:13,270 --> 00:11:14,440
I couldn't even react

168
00:11:14,440 --> 00:11:15,840
before I was knocked out.

169
00:11:17,200 --> 00:11:18,460
So they have the phone?

170
00:11:18,750 --> 00:11:19,720
P-Probably.

171
00:11:20,440 --> 00:11:21,270
It was when I asked them

172
00:11:21,270 --> 00:11:22,080
for the phone

173
00:11:22,390 --> 00:11:23,520
that I was ambushed.

174
00:11:27,080 --> 00:11:27,550
Ren.

175
00:11:32,510 --> 00:11:34,370
Can we trust what Li Penggai said?

176
00:11:37,240 --> 00:11:37,900
I trust him.

177
00:11:38,480 --> 00:11:38,910
Why?

178
00:11:43,270 --> 00:11:44,480
One million dollars.

179
00:11:45,630 --> 00:11:47,080
Because he knows what will happen to him

180
00:11:47,080 --> 00:11:48,340
if he takes your money.

181
00:11:57,420 --> 00:11:58,880
I took my medicine, right?

182
00:11:59,510 --> 00:11:59,870
Okay.

183
00:12:00,630 --> 00:12:01,600
Those two junk collectors

184
00:12:01,600 --> 00:12:02,680
took my phone.

185
00:12:02,960 --> 00:12:03,630
Then those two who robbed me—

186
00:12:03,630 --> 00:12:05,360
why do they still want to
make a deal with me?

187
00:12:05,360 --> 00:12:06,620
They want to kidnap me?

188
00:12:08,240 --> 00:12:09,360
Besides, who could knock him out

189
00:12:09,360 --> 00:12:10,560
with just one strike?

190
00:12:10,790 --> 00:12:11,750
Who is his boss,

191
00:12:12,080 --> 00:12:13,280
and what do they want?

192
00:12:19,670 --> 00:12:20,120
Hello?

193
00:12:20,490 --> 00:12:21,540
Hello, Mr. Zhou.

194
00:12:22,390 --> 00:12:23,450
I thought about it.

195
00:12:23,790 --> 00:12:25,320
Twenty million is too much.

196
00:12:25,600 --> 00:12:26,390
It's appropriate for us,

197
00:12:26,390 --> 00:12:27,270
but not for you.

198
00:12:28,360 --> 00:12:29,220
How about this?

199
00:12:29,440 --> 00:12:30,240
Five million.

200
00:12:31,200 --> 00:12:32,150
10 o'clock.

201
00:12:32,470 --> 00:12:33,550
Five million.

202
00:12:34,270 --> 00:12:35,360
Put it in the trash can

203
00:12:35,360 --> 00:12:36,440
at Sculpture Square.

204
00:12:36,440 --> 00:12:37,100
How's that?

205
00:12:38,440 --> 00:12:38,960
Sure.

206
00:12:40,270 --> 00:12:41,870
Make sure you come and get it.

207
00:12:45,150 --> 00:12:45,670
Rong.

208
00:12:46,360 --> 00:12:47,750
Those two boys are showing mercy.

209
00:12:47,750 --> 00:12:48,790
They said 20 million is too much,

210
00:12:48,790 --> 00:12:50,320
and lowered it to 5 million.

211
00:12:50,550 --> 00:12:51,200
Put it in the trash can

212
00:12:51,200 --> 00:12:52,150
at Sculpture Square

213
00:12:52,150 --> 00:12:52,950
at 10 o'clock.

214
00:12:55,000 --> 00:12:55,530
Mr. Zhou,

215
00:12:56,090 --> 00:12:57,440
this doesn't feel right.

216
00:12:57,440 --> 00:12:58,700
Let's cancel the deal.

217
00:12:58,790 --> 00:12:59,790
Cancel what?

218
00:13:00,000 --> 00:13:01,150
Since they want to play,

219
00:13:01,150 --> 00:13:02,810
I'll play a big game with them.

220
00:13:12,410 --> 00:13:12,880
Drive.

221
00:13:19,090 --> 00:13:22,580
[Sanjiangkou People's Hospital]

222
00:13:24,150 --> 00:13:25,450
What time's lunch?

223
00:13:25,840 --> 00:13:26,460
Bowen,

224
00:13:26,600 --> 00:13:27,600
it's still early.

225
00:13:28,550 --> 00:13:29,700
Go order some fruit.

226
00:13:36,080 --> 00:13:37,840
What are you mulling over now?

227
00:13:39,080 --> 00:13:40,480
Let me sort it out for you.

228
00:13:41,240 --> 00:13:41,670
Bro,

229
00:13:42,030 --> 00:13:43,630
how can you still eat?

230
00:13:44,840 --> 00:13:46,030
If Mr. Zhou doesn't contact us,

231
00:13:46,030 --> 00:13:47,170
can't we just ask him

232
00:13:47,200 --> 00:13:48,910
if he found the phone or not?

233
00:13:50,030 --> 00:13:51,830
Why do I feel like
you are my boss?

234
00:13:52,870 --> 00:13:53,790
Boss, here.

235
00:13:54,160 --> 00:13:55,220
Have some nuts.

236
00:13:58,270 --> 00:14:00,070
Do you think the fruit is for you?

237
00:14:00,390 --> 00:14:01,920
Zhou Rong will be here soon.

238
00:14:04,440 --> 00:14:05,770
Bowen, Mr. Zhou is here.

239
00:14:05,790 --> 00:14:06,390
Let him in.

240
00:14:07,200 --> 00:14:07,730
Mr. Zhou.

241
00:14:10,240 --> 00:14:10,820
Mr. Zhou.

242
00:14:11,030 --> 00:14:11,560
Mr. Zhou.

243
00:14:12,000 --> 00:14:12,530
Jianren.

244
00:14:12,790 --> 00:14:13,240
Ren.

245
00:14:13,670 --> 00:14:14,030
Sit.

246
00:14:14,360 --> 00:14:15,070
Well,

247
00:14:15,200 --> 00:14:16,480
I had someone order some fruit.

248
00:14:16,480 --> 00:14:17,600
What do you want to eat?

249
00:14:17,600 --> 00:14:18,640
What's all this?

250
00:14:18,720 --> 00:14:19,510
I came to see you.

251
00:14:19,510 --> 00:14:20,390
Of course I should be the one
buying things.

252
00:14:20,390 --> 00:14:22,030
How could I let you buy anything?

253
00:14:22,030 --> 00:14:23,290
I brought everything.

254
00:14:28,080 --> 00:14:29,610
Jianren, give me a back rub.

255
00:14:31,270 --> 00:14:32,110
Pound my back!

256
00:14:35,840 --> 00:14:36,440
Yangyang.

257
00:14:36,720 --> 00:14:37,630
You go out first.

258
00:14:37,630 --> 00:14:39,830
Mr. Zhou and I have business to discuss.

259
00:14:40,600 --> 00:14:41,930
Don't leave, Yangyang.

260
00:14:42,550 --> 00:14:43,430
You are not a kid anymore.

261
00:14:43,430 --> 00:14:45,560
You should care about family matters.

262
00:14:45,870 --> 00:14:46,640
Sit down.

263
00:14:54,120 --> 00:14:54,670
Mr. Zhou.

264
00:14:55,850 --> 00:14:57,090
You seem quite angry.

265
00:15:03,070 --> 00:15:04,240
Is it because of

266
00:15:04,270 --> 00:15:06,130
Zhang Yi'ang's visit last night?

267
00:15:07,320 --> 00:15:08,450
Can you explain that

268
00:15:08,790 --> 00:15:10,550
clearly to me?

269
00:15:11,670 --> 00:15:13,480
If I could explain this clearly,

270
00:15:13,960 --> 00:15:16,420
then Zhang Yi'ang
would be too incompetent.

271
00:15:22,150 --> 00:15:23,390
If I told you

272
00:15:23,550 --> 00:15:24,200
he came here last night

273
00:15:24,200 --> 00:15:25,200
making a big scene

274
00:15:25,670 --> 00:15:26,800
but told me nothing—

275
00:15:27,440 --> 00:15:29,150
just wants you to make me doubt you

276
00:15:29,150 --> 00:15:30,720
and cause internal friction—

277
00:15:30,720 --> 00:15:32,050
would you believe that?

278
00:15:45,150 --> 00:15:45,680
Mr. Zhou,

279
00:15:46,360 --> 00:15:47,290
what will it take

280
00:15:48,070 --> 00:15:50,250
for you to believe me?

281
00:15:53,640 --> 00:15:54,810
In 1944,

282
00:15:55,670 --> 00:15:57,400
on the Western Front in Europe,

283
00:15:58,480 --> 00:16:00,940
20 German divisions besieged the Ardennes.

284
00:16:01,440 --> 00:16:03,470
8,000 American soldiers surrendered.

285
00:16:03,470 --> 00:16:04,750
But the 101st Airborne Division

286
00:16:04,750 --> 00:16:05,810
held the line.

287
00:16:06,910 --> 00:16:07,720
In the end,

288
00:16:08,110 --> 00:16:09,640
the Allies won the victory.

289
00:16:10,080 --> 00:16:11,440
Now I am Eisenhower.

290
00:16:12,030 --> 00:16:13,120
Are you willing

291
00:16:13,550 --> 00:16:15,410
to be my 101st Airborne Division?

292
00:16:22,160 --> 00:16:25,160
You know about the battle
of the back mountain, right?

293
00:16:25,870 --> 00:16:27,070
Whose back mountain?

294
00:16:28,720 --> 00:16:30,360
Those 2 guys who snatched the phone

295
00:16:30,360 --> 00:16:31,360
are now asking for 5 million

296
00:16:31,360 --> 00:16:32,110
to redeem the phone.

297
00:16:32,110 --> 00:16:33,790
They asked me to drop
the money at 10 o'clock today...

298
00:16:33,790 --> 00:16:34,630
Sculpture Square.

299
00:16:34,630 --> 00:16:36,000
In the trash can at Sculpture Square.

300
00:16:36,000 --> 00:16:38,080
They will return the phone
when they see the money.

301
00:16:38,080 --> 00:16:39,080
Coincidentally,

302
00:16:39,360 --> 00:16:40,630
Zhu Yifei asked me

303
00:16:40,670 --> 00:16:42,330
to trade the bianzhong today.

304
00:16:44,120 --> 00:16:44,920
So I was hoping

305
00:16:45,360 --> 00:16:46,200
you could help me run

306
00:16:46,200 --> 00:16:47,720
the phone deal errand.

307
00:16:48,530 --> 00:16:49,790
I have the money ready.

308
00:17:15,480 --> 00:17:17,270
As for those two,

309
00:17:17,680 --> 00:17:18,880
do whatever you want.

310
00:17:18,880 --> 00:17:19,760
But the phone,

311
00:17:19,920 --> 00:17:21,050
you must get it back.

312
00:17:23,240 --> 00:17:24,310
If my leg were fine,

313
00:17:24,349 --> 00:17:25,710
I would definitely go.

314
00:17:26,160 --> 00:17:26,960
That's why I had Yangyang

315
00:17:26,960 --> 00:17:27,819
stay, didn't I?

316
00:17:32,030 --> 00:17:32,590
Mr. Zhou.

317
00:17:33,350 --> 00:17:34,480
I can go in his stead.

318
00:17:35,480 --> 00:17:36,240
Shut up.

319
00:17:36,750 --> 00:17:37,870
What?

320
00:17:38,110 --> 00:17:39,550
I can't go, and you can't go—

321
00:17:39,550 --> 00:17:40,640
can't Yangyang go?

322
00:17:41,480 --> 00:17:43,140
Don't want the phone anymore?

323
00:17:44,790 --> 00:17:45,680
Bowen.

324
00:17:46,720 --> 00:17:47,960
You don't care

325
00:17:48,880 --> 00:17:50,440
about this phone at all?

326
00:17:51,510 --> 00:17:53,510
I do care. I care a lot.

327
00:17:54,070 --> 00:17:55,640
But we can't let Yangyang go.

328
00:17:55,640 --> 00:17:56,780
Then who else can go?

329
00:17:57,310 --> 00:17:57,960
Who?

330
00:17:58,200 --> 00:17:59,030
Who else?

331
00:18:00,600 --> 00:18:02,070
I can just give up this phone.

332
00:18:02,070 --> 00:18:02,830
At worst, I'll move somewhere else

333
00:18:02,830 --> 00:18:04,230
and still make a fortune.

334
00:18:04,480 --> 00:18:05,240
But I won't.

335
00:18:05,400 --> 00:18:07,000
I want those bastards to know

336
00:18:07,000 --> 00:18:08,440
that no one can touch my money.

337
00:18:08,440 --> 00:18:09,440
Whoever lays a finger on it,

338
00:18:09,440 --> 00:18:11,040
I'll fight them to the death.

339
00:18:11,310 --> 00:18:12,880
That's my principle.

340
00:18:13,440 --> 00:18:14,310
Look at you.

341
00:18:14,350 --> 00:18:15,550
What have you become?

342
00:18:16,440 --> 00:18:18,000
Are you still the dominating

343
00:18:18,000 --> 00:18:18,750
Bowen?

344
00:18:19,790 --> 00:18:21,080
It's obvious

345
00:18:21,110 --> 00:18:23,030
that someone is targeting us.

346
00:18:23,160 --> 00:18:24,960
Why are you too scared to step up?

347
00:18:25,480 --> 00:18:27,240
Hiding is useless.

348
00:18:27,440 --> 00:18:28,400
If you're done for

349
00:18:28,400 --> 00:18:29,330
and I'm done for,

350
00:18:29,400 --> 00:18:30,660
will Yangyang be fine?

351
00:18:34,070 --> 00:18:35,920
You have quite a few enemies, right?

352
00:18:35,920 --> 00:18:36,590
Without protection,

353
00:18:36,590 --> 00:18:38,250
what will happen to Yangyang?

354
00:18:40,510 --> 00:18:41,270
Bowen,

355
00:18:41,680 --> 00:18:42,550
I think

356
00:18:43,000 --> 00:18:45,000
you should let Yangyang take a chance.

357
00:18:45,000 --> 00:18:46,310
Give him an opportunity

358
00:18:46,310 --> 00:18:47,580
to surprise us all.

359
00:18:47,790 --> 00:18:48,450
How's that?

360
00:18:55,510 --> 00:18:56,020
Bro,

361
00:18:57,130 --> 00:18:58,130
let me go.

362
00:19:05,240 --> 00:19:06,240
Get ready to work.

363
00:19:06,480 --> 00:19:07,080
Yangyang,

364
00:19:07,400 --> 00:19:09,060
I'll wait for you downstairs.

365
00:19:25,690 --> 00:19:26,740
Remember this,

366
00:19:27,350 --> 00:19:28,590
leave no survivors.

367
00:19:29,310 --> 00:19:29,720
Okay.

368
00:19:31,830 --> 00:19:32,690
What about you?

369
00:19:33,160 --> 00:19:33,720
Why?

370
00:19:34,510 --> 00:19:35,370
Do you think another team will pop up

371
00:19:35,370 --> 00:19:36,830
and attack me from behind?

372
00:19:41,440 --> 00:19:42,410
Come here.

373
00:19:50,640 --> 00:19:51,500
Are you stupid?

374
00:19:51,750 --> 00:19:52,510
Huh?

375
00:19:54,680 --> 00:19:55,550
I know

376
00:19:55,590 --> 00:19:56,720
you want to drive Zhou Rong away.

377
00:19:56,720 --> 00:19:58,020
But now is not the time.

378
00:19:58,070 --> 00:19:59,070
That phone is

379
00:19:59,110 --> 00:20:00,070
more important to you than
it is to Zhou Rong.

380
00:20:00,070 --> 00:20:01,200
You don't know shit!

381
00:20:02,350 --> 00:20:03,110
Not to mention the phone

382
00:20:03,110 --> 00:20:04,000
falling into the hands of the police,

383
00:20:04,000 --> 00:20:05,000
even if it's on the national news,

384
00:20:05,000 --> 00:20:06,200
I wouldn't be afraid.

385
00:20:09,070 --> 00:20:09,750
Why?

386
00:20:11,730 --> 00:20:13,710
Because I didn't kill Lu Zheng.

387
00:20:14,070 --> 00:20:15,680
He was hit by a car.

388
00:20:18,030 --> 00:20:19,660
When I was following him,

389
00:20:19,960 --> 00:20:20,830
the phone happened to record

390
00:20:20,830 --> 00:20:21,830
the moment he was hit—

391
00:20:21,830 --> 00:20:22,960
what a coincidence!

392
00:20:23,510 --> 00:20:24,920
I showed the video to Zhou Rong,

393
00:20:24,920 --> 00:20:25,680
saying I did

394
00:20:25,720 --> 00:20:26,400
exactly what he wanted

395
00:20:26,400 --> 00:20:27,860
just to get money from him.

396
00:20:32,030 --> 00:20:32,680
It had absolutely nothing

397
00:20:32,680 --> 00:20:34,240
to do with us in the first place.

398
00:20:34,240 --> 00:20:35,240
If Zhou Rong ran away in fear,

399
00:20:35,240 --> 00:20:36,770
Sanjiangkou would be ours.

400
00:20:37,310 --> 00:20:38,370
It's a great thing.

401
00:20:41,680 --> 00:20:43,680
Now he's forcing me to kill someone.

402
00:20:46,120 --> 00:20:48,180
He couldn't do anything to me before.

403
00:20:48,440 --> 00:20:49,030
But look at you—

404
00:20:49,030 --> 00:20:49,920
you agreed to it.

405
00:20:49,920 --> 00:20:50,850
What do we do now?

406
00:20:58,160 --> 00:20:58,640
Go

407
00:20:59,200 --> 00:21:00,530
a little further later.

408
00:21:00,720 --> 00:21:01,640
Find a payphone

409
00:21:01,680 --> 00:21:02,810
and call the police.

410
00:21:03,270 --> 00:21:05,640
Whatever you do,
don't tell them who you are.

411
00:21:05,640 --> 00:21:06,650
Tell the police

412
00:21:06,680 --> 00:21:07,790
about the phone deal.

413
00:21:07,790 --> 00:21:09,270
If the police catch those two first,

414
00:21:09,270 --> 00:21:10,230
we'll be fine.

415
00:21:11,400 --> 00:21:12,270
Do you hear me?

416
00:21:15,310 --> 00:21:16,170
I can't do that.

417
00:21:18,000 --> 00:21:18,830
Why?

418
00:21:30,550 --> 00:21:31,110
Here,

419
00:21:31,830 --> 00:21:32,430
take this.

420
00:21:34,470 --> 00:21:35,730
Zhu Yifei has a gun too.

421
00:21:36,240 --> 00:21:36,910
You keep it.

422
00:21:37,270 --> 00:21:37,930
I have a way.

423
00:21:43,070 --> 00:21:44,270
I'll take the stairs.

424
00:22:05,480 --> 00:22:06,560
In the future,

425
00:22:06,640 --> 00:22:08,480
don't make decisions on your own.

426
00:22:08,480 --> 00:22:09,210
Ask me first.

427
00:22:10,000 --> 00:22:11,280
The reason I'm your bro

428
00:22:11,310 --> 00:22:12,970
isn't just because I am older.

429
00:22:20,240 --> 00:22:21,040
Bowen.

430
00:22:21,200 --> 00:22:22,550
Why are you the one going?

431
00:22:22,550 --> 00:22:23,410
Are you up to it?

432
00:22:24,270 --> 00:22:25,350
What else can we do?

433
00:22:25,720 --> 00:22:27,270
I'm Number One after all.

434
00:22:28,510 --> 00:22:30,240
You really are a good brother.

435
00:22:32,400 --> 00:22:33,460
Give me your phone.

436
00:22:44,550 --> 00:22:45,240
Charge it.

437
00:22:46,400 --> 00:22:47,130
Use this one.

438
00:22:47,590 --> 00:22:48,850
They will contact you.

439
00:22:53,830 --> 00:22:54,430
Good luck.

440
00:22:55,110 --> 00:22:55,640
Okay.

441
00:23:00,070 --> 00:23:01,080
Lang Bowen is out.

442
00:23:01,110 --> 00:23:02,070
We'll follow him.

443
00:23:02,070 --> 00:23:03,600
You keep an eye on Zhou Rong.

444
00:23:04,510 --> 00:23:05,240
Understood.

445
00:23:14,400 --> 00:23:15,590
Hu Jianren drove away.

446
00:23:15,590 --> 00:23:16,510
We'll follow him.

447
00:23:16,510 --> 00:23:18,370
Team 2, cover the hospital for us.

448
00:23:31,790 --> 00:23:33,000
Will this trick work?

449
00:23:34,030 --> 00:23:34,760
Absolutely.

450
00:23:36,480 --> 00:23:38,350
Tomorrow, I'll say
I've been coughing up blood lately.

451
00:23:38,350 --> 00:23:39,810
I'll wear this vest inside

452
00:23:40,000 --> 00:23:41,930
and go to the hospital for an X-ray.

453
00:23:42,030 --> 00:23:44,070
Mr. Zhou will have to let me go
to the provincial capital

454
00:23:44,070 --> 00:23:45,030
or Beijing for treatment.

455
00:23:45,030 --> 00:23:46,090
Will he believe it?

456
00:23:48,000 --> 00:23:49,830
It'll be a huge black patch on the lungs—

457
00:23:49,830 --> 00:23:50,960
that's lung cancer.

458
00:23:51,550 --> 00:23:53,150
I'm going to get lung cancer.

459
00:24:00,680 --> 00:24:01,400
Ren?

460
00:24:02,240 --> 00:24:02,880
Ren?

461
00:24:03,550 --> 00:24:05,020
I heard at the door

462
00:24:05,400 --> 00:24:07,000
you're getting lung cancer.

463
00:24:08,240 --> 00:24:09,300
I was just kidding.

464
00:24:10,440 --> 00:24:11,240
Come in.

465
00:24:12,910 --> 00:24:13,430
Here.

466
00:24:13,550 --> 00:24:15,410
Ren, please have a seat.

467
00:24:15,590 --> 00:24:16,420
Sit.

468
00:24:48,440 --> 00:24:49,170
Turn around.

469
00:24:54,350 --> 00:24:56,060
This is where your heart is.

470
00:24:57,350 --> 00:24:58,680
This is a heart disease.

471
00:25:01,640 --> 00:25:03,110
Mr. Zhou has already started

472
00:25:03,110 --> 00:25:03,830
suspecting you.

473
00:25:03,830 --> 00:25:05,110
Can you stop asking for

474
00:25:05,110 --> 00:25:06,140
trouble?

475
00:25:06,590 --> 00:25:07,790
What should I do then?

476
00:25:08,400 --> 00:25:09,200
How can I make Mr. Zhou

477
00:25:09,200 --> 00:25:10,330
stop suspecting me?

478
00:25:10,590 --> 00:25:12,190
That's exactly why I'm here.

479
00:25:12,510 --> 00:25:13,440
Last night, Zhu Yifei

480
00:25:13,440 --> 00:25:14,560
called Mr. Zhou,

481
00:25:14,920 --> 00:25:16,750
saying they'll trade the bianzhong today

482
00:25:16,750 --> 00:25:19,410
and specifically asked Mr. Zhou
to go in person.

483
00:25:19,590 --> 00:25:20,070
So,

484
00:25:21,510 --> 00:25:23,510
Mr. Zhou is planning to take him out.

485
00:25:28,830 --> 00:25:31,230
It's too dangerous
for Mr. Zhou to go alone.

486
00:25:31,640 --> 00:25:32,200
How about

487
00:25:33,110 --> 00:25:34,310
you go instead of him?

488
00:25:35,310 --> 00:25:36,030
Ren,

489
00:25:36,640 --> 00:25:37,100
well...

490
00:25:37,720 --> 00:25:38,680
can he not go?

491
00:25:50,480 --> 00:25:51,240
Shall I talk to Mr. Zhou

492
00:25:51,240 --> 00:25:52,440
about this?

493
00:25:56,550 --> 00:25:57,010
I'll go.

494
00:25:58,160 --> 00:25:58,770
I'll go.

495
00:26:00,160 --> 00:26:00,720
Yibo.

496
00:26:01,350 --> 00:26:01,720
Yi...

497
00:26:03,780 --> 00:26:04,980
Change your clothes.

498
00:26:20,610 --> 00:26:22,120
What were you thinking?

499
00:26:28,030 --> 00:26:29,060
Go find Lang Bowen

500
00:26:29,350 --> 00:26:30,550
and ask him to help me.

501
00:26:31,270 --> 00:26:32,330
Just tell him

502
00:26:32,470 --> 00:26:33,510
I will definitely not tell anyone

503
00:26:33,510 --> 00:26:34,510
about what happened

504
00:26:34,510 --> 00:26:36,100
the night Ye Jian died.

505
00:26:36,480 --> 00:26:37,880
Ask him to please help me.

506
00:26:38,400 --> 00:26:39,130
Got it?

507
00:26:39,720 --> 00:26:41,180
You can only tell him this.

508
00:26:42,830 --> 00:26:43,350
Got it.

509
00:26:43,970 --> 00:26:44,730
[Meal Times]

510
00:26:44,160 --> 00:26:44,830
You just have to do the paperwork

511
00:26:44,830 --> 00:26:46,270
at the inpatient department.

512
00:26:46,270 --> 00:26:46,880
Thank you.

513
00:26:53,510 --> 00:26:54,110
Yangyang!

514
00:26:54,880 --> 00:26:55,480
Yangyang!

515
00:26:56,510 --> 00:26:58,170
Which room is your brother in?

516
00:27:02,240 --> 00:27:03,350
Where is your brother?

517
00:27:03,350 --> 00:27:04,060
Where is he?

518
00:27:05,480 --> 00:27:06,740
What's the matter, Qi?

519
00:27:07,960 --> 00:27:08,750
I am looking for him.

520
00:27:08,750 --> 00:27:10,080
His phone is turned off.

521
00:27:11,000 --> 00:27:12,480
My brother is not available right now.

522
00:27:12,480 --> 00:27:13,550
Where is he? Tell me.

523
00:27:13,550 --> 00:27:14,480
There's no time.

524
00:27:15,550 --> 00:27:16,510
My brother went out on an errand.

525
00:27:16,510 --> 00:27:17,240
If there's anything,

526
00:27:17,240 --> 00:27:18,300
you can tell me, Qi.

527
00:27:19,310 --> 00:27:20,590
Yibo is in trouble.

528
00:27:20,960 --> 00:27:22,290
Only Bowen can help him.

529
00:27:22,720 --> 00:27:24,850
When you see your brother, tell him...

530
00:27:26,720 --> 00:27:27,830
Yibo will never tell anyone

531
00:27:27,830 --> 00:27:28,680
what happened

532
00:27:29,790 --> 00:27:31,480
on the night Ye Jian died.

533
00:27:31,790 --> 00:27:33,450
Ask your brother to call Yibo.

534
00:27:34,960 --> 00:27:36,270
B-But my brother won't be back

535
00:27:36,270 --> 00:27:37,780
anytime soon.

536
00:27:46,070 --> 00:27:46,640
Zhang.

537
00:27:47,920 --> 00:27:49,160
Is putting all our attention

538
00:27:49,160 --> 00:27:50,240
on Zhou Rong

539
00:27:50,240 --> 00:27:51,200
and Lang Bowen

540
00:27:51,880 --> 00:27:52,550
a good idea?

541
00:27:53,350 --> 00:27:54,680
What's wrong with that?

542
00:27:57,350 --> 00:27:58,690
When Fang Chao and Liu Zhi

543
00:27:58,690 --> 00:28:00,150
were getting gas earlier,

544
00:28:00,160 --> 00:28:01,110
they tried to pay in US dollars

545
00:28:01,110 --> 00:28:02,110
but got rejected.

546
00:28:02,370 --> 00:28:03,700
Then they went to a hotel

547
00:28:03,880 --> 00:28:05,960
and paid the deposit in US dollars too.

548
00:28:05,960 --> 00:28:07,000
Could it be that they don't have

549
00:28:07,000 --> 00:28:08,660
any Chinese Yuan left on them?

550
00:28:09,590 --> 00:28:10,160
So?

551
00:28:10,880 --> 00:28:12,550
So they will definitely try

552
00:28:12,550 --> 00:28:13,550
to get some money.

553
00:28:13,640 --> 00:28:14,400
How?

554
00:28:16,750 --> 00:28:18,410
How will they try to get money?

555
00:28:25,640 --> 00:28:26,310
The phone.

556
00:28:27,350 --> 00:28:27,790
They still have

557
00:28:27,790 --> 00:28:28,880
that phone.

558
00:28:29,920 --> 00:28:30,830
They will definitely find Zhou Rong

559
00:28:30,830 --> 00:28:31,440
to strike a deal

560
00:28:31,440 --> 00:28:32,900
with this phone for money.

561
00:28:34,000 --> 00:28:34,750
So if we just

562
00:28:34,790 --> 00:28:36,070
keep a close eye on Zhou Rong's gang,

563
00:28:36,070 --> 00:28:37,330
we can catch these two.

564
00:28:38,720 --> 00:28:39,510
Our current plan

565
00:28:39,510 --> 00:28:40,270
is flawless.

566
00:28:40,880 --> 00:28:41,610
Chief Zhang.

567
00:28:44,160 --> 00:28:44,640
Speak.

568
00:28:45,590 --> 00:28:47,070
Just received an anonymous tip

569
00:28:47,070 --> 00:28:48,110
saying Zhou Rong has an

570
00:28:48,110 --> 00:28:49,370
important deal today.

571
00:28:51,030 --> 00:28:52,030
What kind of deal?

572
00:28:52,350 --> 00:28:53,110
They didn't say.

573
00:28:53,110 --> 00:28:54,170
But there's a deal.

574
00:28:57,830 --> 00:28:59,430
Zhou Rong is quite busy, huh?

575
00:28:59,960 --> 00:29:01,030
Keep a close eye on him.

576
00:29:01,030 --> 00:29:02,540
See what he's up to today.

577
00:29:04,960 --> 00:29:07,820
♪ The chance is waiting patiently
in the bowl ♪

578
00:29:08,810 --> 00:29:10,140
♪ Who covered my eyes ♪

579
00:29:10,880 --> 00:29:12,670
♪ I'm full of ideas ♪

580
00:29:26,550 --> 00:29:26,950
Hello?

581
00:29:27,480 --> 00:29:29,610
Put it in the trash can at the entrance.

582
00:29:30,000 --> 00:29:30,480
Put the case

583
00:29:30,480 --> 00:29:31,310
in those two trash cans.

584
00:29:31,310 --> 00:29:31,710
Hurry.

585
00:29:35,750 --> 00:29:37,010
All units, attention.

586
00:29:37,030 --> 00:29:37,880
This is very likely

587
00:29:37,880 --> 00:29:39,340
the location for the deal.

588
00:29:46,440 --> 00:29:47,000
Bowen.

589
00:29:47,640 --> 00:29:48,550
It won't fit.

590
00:29:49,590 --> 00:29:50,240
Useless.

591
00:29:53,480 --> 00:29:55,280
Lang Bowen got out of the car too.

592
00:29:56,550 --> 00:29:57,270
Take that out,

593
00:29:57,270 --> 00:29:58,470
