602
00:30:14,030 --> 00:30:15,430
You only have 10 minutes.

603
00:30:17,110 --> 00:30:17,590
Hello?

604
00:30:19,480 --> 00:30:20,480
Take the case out.

605
00:30:22,690 --> 00:30:23,860
Hurry up.

606
00:30:25,310 --> 00:30:26,570
All units, attention.

607
00:30:26,640 --> 00:30:28,700
