608
00:30:43,550 --> 00:30:44,350
They're here.

609
00:30:45,640 --> 00:30:46,100
I'll go.

610
00:30:46,270 --> 00:30:46,750
Wait.

611
00:31:01,440 --> 00:31:01,920
Hello?

612
00:31:02,070 --> 00:31:03,400
In 20 minutes,

613
00:31:03,480 --> 00:31:04,510
