633
00:32:01,170 --> 00:32:02,270
No way.

634
00:32:03,160 --> 00:32:04,310
I am in the light and you are in the dark.

635
00:32:04,310 --> 00:32:05,370
You want me to go up?

636
00:32:05,920 --> 00:32:07,100
I am not a child.

637
00:32:09,920 --> 00:32:11,440
Mr. Zhou, you are overthinking.

638
00:32:11,440 --> 00:32:14,300
It really is inconvenient
to move it back and forth.

639
00:32:15,510 --> 00:32:17,040
Then you have no sincerity.

640
00:32:34,070 --> 00:32:34,550
Uncle.

641
00:32:35,510 --> 00:32:36,000
I'll go.

642
00:32:54,000 --> 00:32:54,750
Mr. Zhou!

643
00:32:55,720 --> 00:32:56,510
Come down!

644
00:32:57,200 --> 00:32:58,200
