645
00:33:21,200 --> 00:33:21,920
Mr. Zhou?

646
00:33:50,790 --> 00:33:51,400
Bro.

647
00:34:13,820 --> 00:34:14,840
[Police]

648
00:34:18,739 --> 00:34:20,100
[Police]

649
00:34:29,320 --> 00:34:30,179
Get out! Quick!

650
00:34:33,110 --> 00:34:33,770
Stop!

651
00:34:35,800 --> 00:34:36,800
Stop!

652
00:34:46,710 --> 00:34:47,440
Put your hands up!

653
00:34:47,440 --> 00:34:47,980
Hurry up!

654
00:34:55,880 --> 00:34:56,940
Where is Zhou Rong?

655
00:34:57,920 --> 00:34:59,070
Speak. Where is Zhou Rong?

656
00:34:59,070 --> 00:34:59,800
I don't know!

657
00:35:01,670 --> 00:35:02,810
Zhu Yifei is inside.

658
00:35:02,920 --> 00:35:03,630
Cuff them!

659
00:35:03,840 --> 00:35:04,440
Cuff them!

660
00:35:05,170 --> 00:35:06,150
Don't move when you get off later.

661
00:35:06,150 --> 00:35:06,800
Don't move!

662
00:35:06,800 --> 00:35:07,310
Get off!

663
00:35:09,070 --> 00:35:09,570
Go!

664
00:35:10,070 --> 00:35:10,770
Don't move!

665
00:35:11,400 --> 00:35:12,060
Don't move!

666
00:35:12,280 --> 00:35:13,280
Behave yourself.

667
00:35:23,650 --> 00:35:24,720
♪ He is ♪

668
00:35:26,300 --> 00:35:28,670
♪ Too cunning but like a joke ♪

669
00:35:30,090 --> 00:35:31,190
♪ Ha ha ha ♪

670
00:35:32,660 --> 00:35:33,870
♪ He ♪

671
00:35:35,340 --> 00:35:37,780
♪ Wears his glamorous nails ♪

672
00:35:51,000 --> 00:35:51,960
Let's split up for the search.

673
00:35:51,960 --> 00:35:52,440
Okay

674
00:35:54,000 --> 00:35:55,200
♪ Oh, he ♪

675
00:35:56,890 --> 00:36:01,010
♪ A rusted flower etched
across his chest ♪

676
00:36:03,080 --> 00:36:03,970
♪ Oh, he ♪

677
00:36:05,930 --> 00:36:09,080
♪ Says your worldview's still too small ♪

678
00:36:13,010 --> 00:36:16,710
♪ A rat that steals rice—
humans call it cunning ♪

679
00:36:17,610 --> 00:36:21,380
♪ A human who steals honey—
calls the bees hardworking ♪

680
00:36:22,000 --> 00:36:22,510
No.

681
00:36:22,180 --> 00:36:26,130
♪ Absurd, greedy—
self-proclaimed superior beings ♪

682
00:36:26,690 --> 00:36:31,240
♪ Hypocritical, wasteful, hollow—
this gaudy human race ♪

683
00:36:30,070 --> 00:36:30,960
My car!

684
00:36:31,110 --> 00:36:32,040
My car!

685
00:36:32,430 --> 00:36:33,550
Stop!

686
00:36:33,590 --> 00:36:34,400
What's going on?

687
00:36:34,400 --> 00:36:36,190
Someone drove my car away!

688
00:36:34,700 --> 00:36:35,740
♪ Ha ha ha ha ♪

689
00:36:37,230 --> 00:36:38,990
There's no brake!

690
00:36:39,270 --> 00:36:40,300
♪ Ha ha ha ha ♪

691
00:36:40,230 --> 00:36:41,230
Stop right there!

692
00:36:43,570 --> 00:36:44,730
♪ Ha ha ha ha ♪

693
00:37:02,070 --> 00:37:03,140
♪ He is ♪

694
00:37:04,730 --> 00:37:07,380
♪ Too cunning but like a joke ♪

695
00:37:08,510 --> 00:37:09,950
♪ Ha ha ha ♪

696
00:37:11,450 --> 00:37:12,610
♪ He ♪

697
00:37:13,760 --> 00:37:16,480
♪ Wears his glamorous nails ♪

698
00:37:29,480 --> 00:37:30,590
He's dead for sure.

699
00:37:44,190 --> 00:37:44,670
Hello?

700
00:37:45,480 --> 00:37:46,880
I'm at the park entrance.

701
00:37:47,110 --> 00:37:48,770
Put the money in the trash can.

702
00:37:49,590 --> 00:37:50,320
Which one?

703
00:37:50,670 --> 00:37:51,420
Are you blind?

704
00:37:51,420 --> 00:37:52,750
The one at the entrance.

705
00:37:52,960 --> 00:37:54,620
There are two at the entrance.

706
00:37:54,840 --> 00:37:55,670
The red one or the green one?

707
00:37:55,670 --> 00:37:56,470
The green one.

708
00:38:01,840 --> 00:38:03,370
Can you see me now?

709
00:38:03,400 --> 00:38:04,320
Yes, we can.

710
00:38:07,030 --> 00:38:08,630
Is it the one I'm pointing at?

711
00:38:08,670 --> 00:38:09,680
That's the one.

712
00:38:10,670 --> 00:38:12,850
Do you want the darn money or not?

713
00:38:12,960 --> 00:38:15,160
Why are you making me go round and round!

714
00:38:15,590 --> 00:38:16,850
He's quite ticked off.

715
00:38:17,970 --> 00:38:19,020
I have a card

716
00:38:19,050 --> 00:38:20,420
