717
00:38:20,550 --> 00:38:22,900
Take the money and get out of Sanjiangkou.

718
00:38:24,670 --> 00:38:25,190
Hello?

719
00:38:27,480 --> 00:38:28,030
Hello?

720
00:38:29,150 --> 00:38:29,760
He hung up?

721
00:38:30,590 --> 00:38:31,480
Bad guys nowadays

722
00:38:31,480 --> 00:38:33,360
