723
00:38:35,020 --> 00:38:35,590
Get off.

724
00:38:38,460 --> 00:38:39,390
What is he doing?

725
00:38:40,590 --> 00:38:41,510
Thinking of leaving again?

726
00:38:41,510 --> 00:38:42,510
All units, attention.

727
00:38:42,510 --> 00:38:43,910
Get ready to act any time.

728
00:38:44,800 --> 00:38:45,280
Go.

729
00:38:50,920 --> 00:38:51,680
Get off!

730
00:38:51,840 --> 00:38:52,540
Get off!

731
00:39:03,670 --> 00:39:04,730
Out for a breather?

732
00:39:04,800 --> 00:39:07,730
I'm going back to the hospital
to change my dressing.

733
00:39:07,880 --> 00:39:08,860
Wh-What did I do?

734
00:39:09,110 --> 00:39:09,680
Nothing.

735
00:39:09,960 --> 00:39:11,110
Take him back to the station
to change his dressing.

736
00:39:11,110 --> 00:39:11,640
Yes, sir.

737
00:39:11,670 --> 00:39:12,400
Chief Zhang?

738
00:39:12,670 --> 00:39:13,000
Chief Zhang!

739
00:39:13,000 --> 00:39:13,800
Get off.

740
00:39:14,400 --> 00:39:14,710
Wang,

741
00:39:14,710 --> 00:39:16,030
