742
00:39:16,030 --> 00:39:17,590
We caught Hu Jianren and Lu Yibo.

743
00:39:17,590 --> 00:39:19,230
The seller of the bianzhong is Zhu Yifei.

744
00:39:19,230 --> 00:39:19,920
When he was trying to escape,

745
00:39:19,920 --> 00:39:21,850
he fell down the mountain and died.

746
00:39:22,110 --> 00:39:23,190
What about Zhou Rong?

747
00:39:23,190 --> 00:39:24,440
Zhou Rong didn't come at all.

748
00:39:24,440 --> 00:39:26,370
He probably went back to his villa.

749
00:39:27,800 --> 00:39:29,220
We fell for a decoy.

750
00:39:29,630 --> 00:39:30,510
The deal is very likely

751
00:39:30,510 --> 00:39:31,360
taking place at Zhou Rong's villa.

752
00:39:31,360 --> 00:39:32,710
Head to Zhou Rong's villa right away.

753
00:39:32,710 --> 00:39:33,440
Chief Zhang!

754
00:39:33,510 --> 00:39:34,240
Chief Zhang!

755
00:39:34,480 --> 00:39:36,080
You can't treat me like this!

756
00:39:36,230 --> 00:39:37,510
You can't treat me like this,

757
00:39:37,510 --> 00:39:37,960
Chief Zhang.

758
00:39:37,960 --> 00:39:38,920
I just got discharged from the hospital.

759
00:39:38,920 --> 00:39:40,440
How should I treat you, then?

760
00:39:40,440 --> 00:39:41,170
Chief Zhang!

761
00:39:50,400 --> 00:39:51,000
Captain Wang.

762
00:39:51,000 --> 00:39:52,060
Huo Zheng got away.

763
00:39:52,960 --> 00:39:53,760
Didn't he die?

764
00:39:53,880 --> 00:39:54,680
He didn't die.

765
00:39:57,550 --> 00:39:58,280
Chief Zhang.

766
00:39:58,760 --> 00:39:59,760
Huo Zheng is not dead.

767
00:39:59,760 --> 00:40:00,420
He got away.

768
00:40:01,150 --> 00:40:02,280
Arrange a search first,

769
00:40:02,280 --> 00:40:03,940
and then come over right away.

770
00:40:04,440 --> 00:40:05,040
Copy that.

771
00:40:06,070 --> 00:40:06,930
Take them away.

772
00:40:08,710 --> 00:40:09,110
Get up!

773
00:40:09,800 --> 00:40:10,150
Go!

774
00:40:10,170 --> 00:40:10,670
Go!

775
00:40:11,110 --> 00:40:11,550
Move!

776
00:40:19,110 --> 00:40:19,590
Bro.

777
00:40:20,440 --> 00:40:21,370
Do we make a move?

778
00:40:33,590 --> 00:40:35,120
Let's wait a little longer.

779
00:40:37,590 --> 00:40:38,120
Mr. Zhou.

780
00:40:48,710 --> 00:40:49,910
Where did you find it?

781
00:40:50,440 --> 00:40:51,790
In a small alley

782
00:40:51,880 --> 00:40:53,280
not far from the company.

783
00:40:53,280 --> 00:40:54,880
I found it on my way to work just now.

784
00:40:54,880 --> 00:40:55,760
The car wasn't locked

785
00:40:55,760 --> 00:40:57,110
and the keys were still in the ignition,

786
00:40:57,110 --> 00:40:58,110
so I drove it back.

787
00:40:59,400 --> 00:41:01,400
You didn't sleep all night, did you?

788
00:41:02,110 --> 00:41:03,510
This car has a GPS tracker.

789
00:41:03,510 --> 00:41:05,230
It hasn't stopped since yesterday.

790
00:41:05,230 --> 00:41:07,190
It almost drove out of Sanjiangkou.

791
00:41:07,190 --> 00:41:08,960
So how did you find it

792
00:41:08,960 --> 00:41:09,890
in a small alley?

793
00:41:19,400 --> 00:41:21,510
You've been undercover
next to me for so many years.

794
00:41:21,510 --> 00:41:23,040
I didn't expect it to be you.

795
00:41:24,020 --> 00:41:24,840
Wait.

796
00:41:26,480 --> 00:41:27,320
Don't do it here.
